      "topics": [
        {
          "id": "overview",
          "title": "Winter Themes",
          "content": "# Winter Themes\n\nA collection of five winter-inspired color themes for Clubhouse.\n\n## Themes\n\n### Frost (Light)\nCrisp ice-blue tones with pale, frosty backgrounds. A clean, cool theme like a frozen windowpane at dawn.\n\n### Evergreen (Light)\nDeep pine greens on soft snowy whites — a walk through a quiet evergreen forest blanketed in snow.\n\n### Northern Lights (Dark)\nAurora borealis on a dark arctic sky. Vivid greens, purples, and cyans dance across a deep navy background. Enhanced with an aurora background gradient and a green-to-purple accent gradient.\n\n### Snowfall (Light)\nUltra-minimal and serene. Nearly pure white with the faintest blue-gray tints, like fresh snowfall on a still morning. Uses a clean Helvetica Neue font.\n\n### Polar Night (Dark)\nThe deep, cold blue of an arctic winter night. Muted, desaturated accents against a rich navy canvas. Features a deep polar blue background gradient.\n\n## Usage\n\nInstall the plugin and select any Winter Theme from **Settings > Appearance > Theme**."
        }
      ]
